# Privacy Policy

**xkcd for iOS**

Last updated: December 24, 2025

## Overview

xkcd for iOS is a free app that lets you browse xkcd comics. We do not collect, store, or share any personal information.

## Data Collection

This app does not collect any data from users. We do not track you, require an account, or gather analytics.

## Third-Party Content

All comics displayed in this app are created by Randall Munroe and are licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial 2.5 License. The comics are fetched directly from xkcd.com. Your interaction with this content is subject to xkcd's own terms and privacy practices.

## Network Requests

The app connects to xkcd.com to retrieve comic images and metadata. We do not operate any servers and do not intercept or log these requests.

## Changes to This Policy

If this policy changes, the updated version will be posted here with a new date.
